      "content": "Those feelings of helplessness and the weight of perceived failure are completely understandable given the magnitude of what you are facing. While no one can magically erase the debt or the past, focusing only on the catastrophe prevents you from seeing potential paths forward. Please allow someone trustworthy, like a therapist, to help you manage the immediate emotional crisis so you can begin to see even tiny possible next steps. You are not a catastrophe; you are someone navigating an extreme crisis.",
      "source": "target",
